title: Advanced Atomics Fixed
author: drbert+madurban, nihilistzsche
description: Advanced Atomics provides you with improved versions of ammunition, armor and equipment made from Uranium or Plutonium-239. Research advanced atomic processes like Plutonium Nucleosynthesis to synthesize Pu-239 or Uranium Extraction to extract uranium from copper, iron or water.
